policy_text: Basic insurance coverage is mandatory and includes: Collision Damage Waiver (CDW), Third Party Liability (TPL), and Personal Accident Insurance (PAI). Daily rate varies by vehicle class.
Premium insurance package includes basic coverage plus: Zero deductible, Tire and glass coverage, Personal effects coverage, and Roadside assistance. Available for an additional $15/day.
Renters must be at least 21 years old, possess a valid driver's license, and present a major credit card. Additional fees apply for drivers under 25.
